episodes.title: Louis Theroux on Scientology, Success, Regrets, Religion and His Upcoming Series
episodes.description:
I managed to get a couple of minutes with the worlds favourite documentarian - Louis Theroux. We had a chat about the release of his latest film My Scientology Movie as well as it's phenomenal success at the British box office. Louis also talks regrets, David Miscavige, Marty Rathbun, the current political climate and offers a glimpse at his upcoming projects involving crime, heroin and sex trafficking. 

You can watch our original interview here - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6E2gf-bzKi8

As always feel free to subscribe for more.

Follow me on Twitter and Instagram - @AshTulett
